{
  "stem": "12494.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah-- so, as I mentioned before, there were two organizations which supported the refugees, the Orthodox, and the Zionists.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Orthodox were a small minority in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the countryside they were quite numerous, but less active politically.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Zionists were a small minority among the non-orthodox.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The two organizations, the Orthodox [NON-ENGLISH], the Orthodox Committee for Refugees, and the Zionist Committee for Refugees, originally did not cooperate with each other.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the reason for that was that Hungarian Orthodox leadership, which was extremely right-wing, did not approve of cooperating with non-Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as the news became worse and worse from the surrounding countries, there was a movement among the Orthodox, headed by my father, to cooperate with the Zionists.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so he had a number of informal meetings with Dr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Kasztner, who was the head of the Zionist Rescue Organization.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It went very slowly, because the Satmar rebbe, who was also among those who returned to Hungary from Romania with the Hitler decision of 1940, and who became the Rabbinic Supreme Authority in Hungarian orthodoxy, objected to any cooperation with the non-Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he's threatened my father with excommunication, with putting him into a herem, if he cooperated with the non-Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So things are dragging on for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then interfered a friend of my father, the son of the chief rabbi of Budapest, chief Orthodox rabbi of Budapest-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went to see the Satmar rebbe and explained to him that this was a question of life and death.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that it was important to cooperate with the non-Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Satmar rabbi relented.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so from then on Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kasztner and my dad, and their respective committees, could work together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And did you attend any of those meetings?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was too young to attend the meetings.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
